153
00:10:22,119 --> 00:10:24,620
He's a perfect lover.

154
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:30,099
- That's not what I mean. You have many strengths, too.
- Don't need to comfort me. That's fine.

155
00:10:30,099 --> 00:10:32,619
Just like... Hey, little Qi Qi.

156
00:10:32,619 --> 00:10:35,379
Come here. Come over here.

157
00:10:35,379 --> 00:10:39,059
Take a look at our big brother Wang Jing!

158
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:41,139
Isn't he a good man?

159
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:43,730
Oh, that's right.

160
00:10:44,370 --> 00:10:46,579
