162
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:54,349
No, no, no! What a weak teammate!

163
00:10:54,350 --> 00:10:56,480
- Wang Jing!
- Where are you going?

164
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,880
Big Bro Jing!

165
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:01,100
