Work routine.

167
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:07,529
You guys are quite interesting.

168
00:11:07,530 --> 00:11:09,820
I'm very happy to be working with you all.

169
00:11:10,790 --> 00:11:14,469
Actually, it's quite interesting to discuss with you.

170
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:17,450
So are we considered friends?

171
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:20,310
Sorry, it may be too sudden.

172
00:11:20,310 --> 00:11:22,790
Maybe we can make friends from now on?

173
00:11:25,550 --> 00:11:28,610
I'll take that as a yes then?

174
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:33,249
That's not right.

175
00:11:33,249 --> 00:11:35,309
He's so nice.

176
00:11:35,309 --> 00:11:37,650
How could I hate him?

177
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:45,739
- Hello?
- Hi.

178
00:11:45,739 --> 00:11:47,500
Yi Zi Tong?

179
00:11:47,500 --> 00:11:49,680
Did I scare you?

180
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:53,009
You didn't, but why do you want to talk to me?

181
00:11:53,009 --> 00:11:55,879
Nothing. I'm just wondering

182
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:59,020
what you wanted to say since you said you had something to tell me.

183
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,570
Thank you.

184
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:11,489
Real can't drink whiskey.

185
00:12:11,489 --> 00:12:14,470
It must be quite inconvenient for you to live together, right?

186
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:16,990
I'm used to it.

187
00:12:17,609 --> 00:12:19,170
So am I.

188
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:30,110
I believe Jin Yu Zhen has been thinking about you all this time.

189
00:12:33,370 --> 00:12:35,480
That's why I came here for him.

190
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:40,280
Do you still love him then?

191
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:43,009
It doesn't matter if I love him,

192
00:12:43,010 --> 00:12:46,090
but what I want to know is if he still loves me.

193
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:48,670
How are you going to confirm it?

194
00:12:50,730 --> 00:12:54,969
Or... have you confirmed it?

195
00:12:57,260 --> 00:13:00,779
He can't tell me the truth right now.

196
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:02,980
