197
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:09,750
Yes, he's very hard to get along with.

198
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:12,970
Did you really complain just now?

199
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:16,850
Not really.

200
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:24,119
So seven years ago, you just

201
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,990
left like that?

202
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:30,220
My family arranged for me to be an intern at the subsidiary in America.

203
00:13:30,220 --> 00:13:33,019
That was a great opportunity.

204
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:35,809
But didn't you discuss it with Jin Yu Zhen first?

205
00:13:35,809 --> 00:13:38,029
I'm not the kind of person who just sits around.

206
00:13:38,029 --> 00:13:41,349
Be it love or work. I'm not satisfied with the status quo.

207
00:13:41,350 --> 00:13:44,600
Of course, Real is aware of it.

208
00:13:46,990 --> 00:13:49,140
I just didn't realize

209
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:52,519
