210
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:54,699
Because he loves you.

211
00:13:54,699 --> 00:13:56,530
I know.

212
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:02,400
That's why he tried so hard to rush to the airport the day I flew out.

213
00:14:04,570 --> 00:14:07,750
But he ended up in a serious car accident.

214
00:14:08,400 --> 00:14:11,319
I remember when he was in university,

215
00:14:11,319 --> 00:14:13,299
