216
00:14:13,299 --> 00:14:16,629
But I heard that he was in a car crash later on.

217
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:18,890
Car crash...

218
00:14:19,899 --> 00:14:21,909
That point in time was too much of a coincidence.

219
00:14:21,910 --> 00:14:24,869
I don't know where he got the news from.

220
00:14:24,869 --> 00:14:28,010
There's an 80% chance that it's Chairman Mai. After all, we all know one another.

221
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,120
I didn't know until later on

222
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,530
that he had been in a coma in the hospital for six months.

223
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:39,010
After he'd come to, he was depressed for a while.

224
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:44,180
So this is

225
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:47,200
how he got his scar.

226
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:52,450
Is his scar very serious?

227
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:06,179
Then he worked so hard to develop his career and network.

228
00:15:06,179 --> 00:15:09,540
He wanted to catch up with me in another way.

229
00:15:10,059 --> 00:15:13,819
Are you saying Jin Yu Zhen wanted to catch up with you?

230
00:15:13,819 --> 00:15:15,640
Isn't it obvious?

231
00:15:15,650 --> 00:15:19,149
He's allergic to nickel, but because of my family background,

232
00:15:19,149 --> 00:15:21,369
he started to be really interested

233
00:15:21,370 --> 00:15:23,679
in products made from metallic minerals.

234
00:15:23,679 --> 00:15:26,229
Now he's even taken over Jingcherng Metalwork and Design.

235
00:15:26,229 --> 00:15:29,630
All the things he's done were making me come here to him.

236
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:35,490
If he hadn't expected the possibility that we would meet again,

237
00:15:37,690 --> 00:15:40,050
then all the things he's done

238
00:15:40,050 --> 00:15:42,270
would be hard to justify.

239
00:15:50,710 --> 00:15:52,660
The Single Rule...

240
00:15:54,160 --> 00:15:55,790
Sorry.

241
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:59,420
It's affected you all because of us both.

242
00:16:01,440 --> 00:16:03,880
The Fragrance of B612.

243
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:07,950
"The Little Prince." Have you heard of it?

244
00:16:09,090 --> 00:16:13,909
Yes, I have. He loved the rose, but...

245
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:16,309
did the rose love him?

246
00:16:16,310 --> 00:16:18,689
Does this piece of work have a name?

247
00:16:18,689 --> 00:16:20,860
The Fragrance of B612.

248
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:25,810
What the Little Prince missed the most

249
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:31,790
was still that rose.

250
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:38,279
Compared with Superman, who couldn't go back to Krypton after it was destroyed,

251
00:16:38,279 --> 00:16:40,379
at least he had the rose.

